From: James Zhu <James.Zhu@amd.com>
Date: Mon, 10 Feb 2020 10:28:00 -0500
Subject: drm/amdgpu: enable VCN2.5 DPG mode for Arcturus
Git-commit: e520859cde724ea451561520ceceb5a630eef4f2
Patch-mainline: v5.8-rc1
References: jsc#SLE-12680, jsc#SLE-12880, jsc#SLE-12882, jsc#SLE-12883, jsc#SLE-13496, jsc#SLE-15322

Enable VCN2.5 DPG mode for arcturus after below items are applied.
ASD: 0x21000023
SOS: 0x17003B
VCN firmware Version ENC: 1.1 DEC: 1 VEP: 0 Revision: 16
VBIOS: 23

Signed-off-by: James Zhu <James.Zhu@amd.com>
Reviewed-by: Leo Liu <leo.liu@amd.com>
Signed-off-by: Alex Deucher <alexander.deucher@amd.com>
Signed-off-by: Patrik Jakobsson <pjakobsson@suse.de>
---
 drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/soc15.c | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/soc15.c b/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/soc15.c
index dc7d83e29938..58a440a15525 100644
--- a/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/soc15.c
+++ b/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/soc15.c
@@ -1217,7 +1217,7 @@ static int soc15_common_early_init(void *handle)
 			AMD_CG_SUPPORT_IH_CG |
 			AMD_CG_SUPPORT_VCN_MGCG |
 			AMD_CG_SUPPORT_JPEG_MGCG;
-		adev->pg_flags = 0;
+		adev->pg_flags = AMD_PG_SUPPORT_VCN | AMD_PG_SUPPORT_VCN_DPG;
 		adev->external_rev_id = adev->rev_id + 0x32;
 		break;
 	case CHIP_RENOIR:
